    <h2>2. Striped Table</h2>
    <p>Alternate row colors for better readability.</p>

    <h3>Code Example:</h3>
    <pre><code>
tr:nth-child(even) {
    background-color: #f2f2f2;
}
tr:hover {
    background-color: #ddd;
}
    </code></pre>

