    <h2>3. Centered Table with Rounded Borders</h2>
    <p>Use <code>margin</code> and <code>border-radius</code> to improve appearance.</p>

    <h3>Code Example:</h3>
    <pre><code>
table {
    margin: auto;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
}
th, td {
    border: 1px solid #333;
    padding: 12px;
}
th {
    background-color: #2196F3;
    color: white;
}
tr:nth-child(even) {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
}
    </code></pre>

    <h3>Result:</h3>
    <table style="margin:auto; border-collapse: collapse; border-radius:10px; overflow:hidden;">
